het MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" ><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/7/Snapchat-62162697.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"900\" data-original-width=\"1600\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">We got in Friday night and it was too windy for any balloons to do a glow so we just got dinner and went to where we were staying for the night (Couchsurfing) and went to bed. The next morning started early and the weather was good to fly luckily!</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" ><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/7/Snapchat-815444451.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"320\" border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1600\" data-original-width=\"900\" /></a><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" ><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/7/Snapchat-882662199.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"320\" border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1600\" data-original-width=\"900\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">The park was by a firehouse and the firemen lifted the ladder high in to the air with the USA flag on it so we could salute and do a National Anthem before the balloons inflated.</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" ><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/7/Snapchat-2125999487.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"900\" data-original-width=\"1600\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; t