; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Some cool owl art at the Sell-A-Rama festival going on</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" ><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/26/IMG_20180129_090224_917.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"272\" border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"720\" data-original-width=\"1054\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">It was super great to see Joey and catch up with her. We had a safe trip back and got to Ridgecrest around 11pm I think. It was worth the extra time spent in Quartzite, for sure!</span></div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>','After the morning balloon flights were done and everything put away, we went back to my sister\'s place where Tony spent some time jumping on the trampoline with my niece and nephew.','2018-02-08 12:18:51','2018-05-12 19:19:56','2018-05-12 23:20:25',NULL),(27,2,'travel',0,'Sunday Morning Balloon Ride','<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\