dth=\"900\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: xx-small;\">Photo by Tony Hoxsie</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: xx-small;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">It was so nice to see green!</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" ><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/63/20170715_102246.jpg\" width=\"225\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1600\" data-original-width=\"900\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: xx-small;\">Photo by Tony Hoxsie</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font