&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" ><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/63/Snapchat-376144419.jpg\" width=\"225\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1600\" data-original-width=\"900\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">So...lesson learned. Never visit Yosemite in the middle of summer. You\'ll be stuck with long delays and no place / hard to find parking. Their shuttle bus system was complicated and we never made it in to a visitors center to get help. I am looking forward to going back in a few months when things have settled down. That all being said - I had some friends in the park that day with their 2 kids and they had a blast. Did not seem to have problems so I will have to message her what their trick was!</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>','We headed to Yosemite from our campsite in a little place called Tuttletown.','2017-07-11 15:47:15','2018-05-12 22:48:10','2018-05-12 23:30:35',NULL),(64,2,'travel',0,'Mossy Cave Trail Water Fun','<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decor