.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-25zQtGAS3JY/UgK_7glkzaI/AAAAAAAA1Ac/0sZfZYxUQkA/s1600/camp3.JPG\"><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/124/camp3.JPG\" width=\"400\" height=\"298\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Here\'s a view from the other side. We could open the back of the teardrop inside the tent and prepare and eat breakfast inside the tent. Another handy thing to do if it had been raining.&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #66cccc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DL85rcLHzgk/UgK_8uCALjI/AAAAAAAA1Ao/ZNYsJTYTd08/s1600/camp4.JPG\"><img style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative;\" src=\"/images/blog/124/camp4.JPG\" width=\"400\" height=\"298\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Trebuchet, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Here is the current look of the back of our teardop. I hope we can get some cupboards put back in there soon. The tupperware containers we got and our ice chest fit pretty perfectly in the bottom section.</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', Tre